 Hi, I'm Charles Chu.  Once a week, I send an edition of  The  Open Circle  newsletter to 20,000+ readers. It can include my best essays for the week, books I love, useful resources, random musings I've had, and much more. It's free. There's no spam ever. And you can unsubscribe anytime. 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
